## Step 2: Prepare Local Directory

On your computer (Linux or Windows):

```bash
# Create working directory
mkdir ~/ipad-a2316-reset
cd ~/ipad-a2316-reset

# Initialize git
git init
git config user.name "Brian Vargo"
git config user.email "your-email@example.com"
```

