## Troubleshooting GitHub Publishing

| Problem | Solution |
|---------|----------|
| "fatal: The current branch main has no upstream branch" | Run `git push -u origin main` (includes the `-u` flag) |
| "could not read Username" | Use SSH key instead of HTTPS, or generate Personal Access Token |
| Files not showing on GitHub | Run `git push origin main` to force sync |
| LICENSE not recognized | Ensure file is named exactly `LICENSE` (no extension) |

